'''Bariga Afrika''' ({{lang-en|East Africa}}; {{lang-ar|شرق أفريقيا}}) waa gobolka dhaca [[bari]]ga qaarada [[Afrika]], taasi oo aad ugu kala duwan deegaan ahaan, juquraafi ahaan iyo siyaasad ahaan. Sida ku xusan qawaaniinta gobolada ee dejisay [[QM|Jimciyada Qarama Midoobay]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://unstats.un.org/unsd/methods/m49/m49regin.htm| title = Composition of macro geographical (continental) regions, geographical sub-regions, and selected economic and other groupings | publisher = United Nations| date = 2013-10-31 | accessdate = 2015-01-28}}</ref> deegaanka Bariga Afrika waxay ka kooban tahay ilaa 20 wadan<ref>{{cite web|url=http://millenniumindicators.un.org/unsd/methods/m49/m49regin.htm|title=United Nations Statistics Division- Standard Country and Area Codes Classifications (M49)|work=un.org}}</ref>, kuwaasi oo kala ah:

* [[Tanzania]], [[Kenya]], [[Uganda]], [[Rwanda]], [[Burundi]] iyo [[Koonfurta Suudaan]] – wadanadan oo dhaca Badhtamaha Bariga Afrika waxay dhammaan xubin ka yihiin ururka [[Bulshada Bariga Afrika]] (East African Community) (EAC).
* [[Soomaaliya]], [[Djibouti], [[Eritrea]] iyo [[Ethiopia]]– dhowrkan wadan waxaa loo yaqaana [[Geeska Afrika]].<ref>Robert Stock, ''Africa South of the Sahara, Second Edition: A Geographical Interpretation'', (The Guilford Press: 2004), p. 26</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.irinnews.org/Africa-Region.aspx?Region=HOA&Service=ENG|title=IRIN - Horn of Africa|work=IRINnews}}</ref><ref>Michael Hodd, ''East Africa Handbook'', 7th Edition, (Passport Books: 2002), p. 21: "To the north are the countries of the Horn of Africa comprising Ethiopia, Eritrea, Djibouti and Somalia."</ref><ref>Encyclopædia Britannica, inc, Jacob E. Safra, ''The New Encyclopædia Britannica'', (Encyclopædia Britannica: 2002), p.61: "The northern mountainous area, known as the Horn of Africa, comprises Djibouti, Ethiopia, Eritrea, and Somalia."</ref>
* [[Comoros]], [[Mauritius]] iyo [[Seychelles]] – kuwani waa gasiirado ku dhex yaala [[Badweynta Hindiya]].
* Réunion iyo Mayotte – gasiirado yaryar oo gacanta ku hayso wadanka [[Faransiiska]].
* [[Mozambique]] iyo [[Madagascar]] – kuwaasi oo marar badan lagu xisaabiyo wadanada [[Koonfurta Afrika]].
* [[Malawi]], [[Zambia]] iyo [[Zimbabwe]].

==Faalo Kooban==

Bariga Afrika waa bariga Qaarada [[Afrika]]:
* [[Soomaaliya]], [[Jabuuti]], [[Eratareya]] iyo [[Itoobiya]], oo iyagana marka laso gaabiyo lagu magacaabo wadamada [[Geeska Afrika]]. 
* [[Tansaaniya]], [[Kiinya]], [[Yugandha]], [[Ruwanda]] iyo [[Burundi]], iyadoona Ruwaanda iyo Burundi mar marka qaarkood lagu daro wadamada ku yaala bartamaha [[Afrika]].

